          <span class="bit w-1 z-20 h-1 opacity-0 transition-all duration-300 absolute transform mt-5 ml-5 -rotate-45 bg-cyan-500 ease-in-out"></span>
          <span class="inline-block skew-x-12 h-2 bit w-1 z-20 opacity-0 transition-all duration-300 absolute transform -rotate-12 bg-lime-500 ease-in-out"></span>
